                        "hint": "Use the assignment operator to assign the value",
                        "correctFeedback": "Perfect! You used the assignment operator correctly.",
                        "incorrectFeedback": "Use = to assign the value to the variable",
                        "explanation": "The = sign assigns values to variables.",
                        "output": "blue"
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
